585
00:19:13,500 --> 00:19:14,440
Okay.

586
00:19:20,420 --> 00:19:21,220
I have decided

587
00:19:21,859 --> 00:19:23,339
to come to Yangliu Xincheng

588
00:19:23,539 --> 00:19:25,019
to spend the rest of my life.

589
00:19:25,279 --> 00:19:26,039
You know, here at our place,

590
00:19:26,039 --> 00:19:27,240
another old man has arrived.

591
00:19:27,599 --> 00:19:29,079
They say he's a university professor.

592
00:19:29,920 --> 00:19:31,640
Knowledgeable and dignified.

593
00:19:31,640 --> 00:19:32,720
Such a handsome old fellow.

594
00:19:32,799 --> 00:19:34,579
Ms. Liu went to show him around.

595
00:19:36,759 --> 00:19:37,500
Over there.

596
00:19:37,779 --> 00:19:38,579
Ms. Liu,

597
00:19:39,420 --> 00:19:42,259
it's rare for you and me to have such a chance,

598
00:19:42,420 --> 00:19:43,460
such a time,

599
00:19:44,019 --> 00:19:46,099
to stroll amidst this beautiful scenery.

600
00:19:46,759 --> 00:19:47,599
Xiao Zhi,

601
00:19:48,680 --> 00:19:50,400
let's hurry and get into character.

602
00:19:50,759 --> 00:19:52,599
Let's find that feeling of passionate love.

603
00:19:55,299 --> 00:19:57,220
At our age,

604
00:19:57,579 --> 00:19:58,559
even if we fall in love,

605
00:19:58,900 --> 00:19:59,539
do you really think

606
00:20:00,140 --> 00:20:01,900
it can be like it is for you young people?

607
00:20:03,819 --> 00:20:04,859
It's nothing more than...

608
00:20:06,500 --> 00:20:07,900
she glanced at me one extra time,

609
00:20:09,180 --> 00:20:10,420
stayed with me a little longer,

610
00:20:12,339 --> 00:20:13,619
or said a few more words.

611
00:20:14,759 --> 00:20:15,859
And inside my heart,

612
00:20:16,039 --> 00:20:17,079
it just feels all warm.

613
00:20:18,019 --> 00:20:19,359
I can be happy all night,

614
00:20:20,019 --> 00:20:21,299
and savor it for days.

615
00:20:23,900 --> 00:20:24,900
That is all.

616
00:20:25,240 --> 00:20:26,339
The sunset is glowing red.

617
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:30,640
I have had no children all my life.

618
00:20:31,119 --> 00:20:32,359
Lonely and solitary.

619
00:20:32,359 --> 00:20:33,480
I never expected that in my old age...

620
00:20:33,480 --> 00:20:34,259
Auntie Liu,

621
00:20:34,259 --> 00:20:35,720
please don't say that.

622
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:37,000
Our community here

623
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:38,359
is a home for the elderly.

624
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:40,519
And we are your family.

625
00:20:40,640 --> 00:20:41,400
Li Zong,

626
00:20:41,839 --> 00:20:43,640
think of a brilliant plan for me too,

627
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:45,680
to get my son to come visit me.

628
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:48,380
Ideally, bringing my little grandson along.

629
00:20:48,579 --> 00:20:49,160
Jingjing,

630
00:20:50,019 --> 00:20:51,559
as long as you still acknowledge me as your dad,

631
00:20:51,839 --> 00:20:53,019
whatever you ask me to do,

632
00:20:53,339 --> 00:20:54,380
I will agree to it.

633
00:20:54,559 --> 00:20:55,299
Son,

634
00:20:55,539 --> 00:20:56,900
I am your father.

635
00:20:57,740 --> 00:20:59,900
Was it easy giving you life and raising you?

636
00:21:08,339 --> 00:21:09,500
Children,

637
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:11,119
actually, Grandma just...

638
00:21:12,319 --> 00:21:13,599
just wants to

639
00:21:13,759 --> 00:21:15,700
chat with you all together,

640
00:21:15,700 --> 00:21:16,960
and have a talk.

641
00:21:17,099 --> 00:21:18,259
Don't lecture me.

642
00:21:18,779 --> 00:21:20,900
Didn't you also abandon your wife?

643
00:21:21,440 --> 00:21:22,460
We are different.

644
00:21:22,819 --> 00:21:25,420
I was abandoned by my wife.

645
00:21:25,900 --> 00:21:28,940
Isn't your department beauty still alive, at least?

646
00:21:30,380 --> 00:21:31,799
My cousin...

647
00:21:34,859 --> 00:21:37,059
we are separated by death.

648
00:21:38,180 --> 00:21:39,500
But in my heart,

649
00:21:40,259 --> 00:21:41,619
she is already gone.

650
00:21:42,539 --> 00:21:44,180
I am living a life worse than death right now.

651
00:21:44,920 --> 00:21:46,019
Major life decisions

652
00:21:46,740 --> 00:21:48,279
must be made by yourself,

653
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:49,799
so you won't regret them in the future.

654
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:52,740
When young, parents interfere;

655
00:21:53,619 --> 00:21:55,660
when old, children interfere.

656
00:21:56,460 --> 00:21:57,819
We want to be together,

657
00:21:58,099 --> 00:21:59,619
why is it just so hard?

658
00:22:00,019 --> 00:22:00,640
Look at this.

659
00:22:00,740 --> 00:22:01,700
Is it easy?

660
00:22:02,240 --> 00:22:03,579
Who would have thought?

661
00:22:04,240 --> 00:22:06,000
The tea cools as soon as the person leaves.

662
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:07,680
Let me tell you,

663
00:22:07,839 --> 00:22:09,799
once you walk into this village,

664
00:22:09,839 --> 00:22:11,640
and live in this courtyard,

665
00:22:11,720 --> 00:22:14,519
we are all one family.

666
00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:17,059
Because you are all my eternal,

667
00:22:17,279 --> 00:22:18,420
best friends.

668
00:22:31,759 --> 00:22:32,599
Dear elders,

669
00:22:33,240 --> 00:22:34,980
what do you think?

670
00:22:35,079 --> 00:22:36,640
Should we delete this video or not?

671
00:22:37,559 --> 00:22:38,099
Well...

672
00:22:38,180 --> 00:22:38,720
you say it.

673
00:22:41,660 --> 00:22:42,660
How about

674
00:22:43,940 --> 00:22:44,539
we just

675
00:22:44,779 --> 00:22:45,900
use their candid footage.

676
00:22:47,440 --> 00:22:48,200
In my personal opinion,

677
00:22:48,200 --> 00:22:48,940
just my personal opinion,

678
00:22:48,980 --> 00:22:49,660
personal opinion.

679
00:22:50,940 --> 00:22:52,660
All the grandpas and grandmas share this opinion.

680
00:22:53,559 --> 00:22:53,920
Ms. Liu,

681
00:22:53,920 --> 00:22:54,700
well, um...

682
00:22:56,759 --> 00:22:57,619
I think

683
00:22:58,279 --> 00:22:59,359
the filming

684
00:23:00,220 --> 00:23:00,859
is actually quite good,

685
00:23:02,279 --> 00:23:03,440
except

686
00:23:03,500 --> 00:23:04,519
if you could just cut that shot

687
00:23:04,519 --> 00:23:06,299
where I'm grinning with my mouth wide open.

688
00:23:07,839 --> 00:23:09,160
I disagree with that.

689
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:11,339
I think Ms. Liu looks best when she laughs.

690
00:23:13,079 --> 00:23:14,299
On this point,

691
00:23:14,359 --> 00:23:16,460
I'm in unprecedented agreement with Old Li.

692
00:23:19,380 --> 00:23:20,259
Ms. Liu looks beautiful no matter how she laughs.

693
00:23:20,259 --> 00:23:20,660
Okay.

694
00:23:20,799 --> 00:23:22,880
Then, dear elders, you can go back and rest.

695
00:23:23,059 --> 00:23:24,920
We'll edit the final version as soon as possible

696
00:23:24,980 --> 00:23:26,240
and ask you to review it one more time.

697
00:23:26,599 --> 00:23:27,420
No need to review it again.

698
00:23:28,059 --> 00:23:29,480
After all the work you've put in,

699
00:23:29,700 --> 00:23:31,319
I already fully trust

700
00:23:31,400 --> 00:23:33,559
the aesthetic taste of you young people.

701
00:23:34,140 --> 00:23:34,640
Right.

702
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:35,059
That's right.

703
00:23:35,599 --> 00:23:36,559
I won't review it either.

704
00:23:36,839 --> 00:23:37,779
After editing,

705
00:23:37,900 --> 00:23:39,039
give everyone a copy

706
00:23:39,180 --> 00:23:41,099
to cherish as a fond memory.

707
00:23:41,299 --> 00:23:42,839
Yes.

708
00:23:42,839 --> 00:23:43,799
Make it a bit longer.

709
00:23:43,900 --> 00:23:44,900
I disagree.

710
00:23:46,859 --> 00:23:47,559
Please speak.

711
00:23:48,140 --> 00:23:49,940
We must add a few more shots.

712
00:23:50,480 --> 00:23:51,420
I've prepared a whole bunch

713
00:23:51,420 --> 00:23:52,839
of photos of my daughter.
